{"tha-ap544:0.1":"Therapadana ","tha-ap544:0.2":"Bhaddiyavagga ","tha-ap544:0.3":"Kankharevatattheraapadana ","tha-ap544:1.1":"“Padumuttaro nama jino, ","tha-ap544:1.2":"sabbadhammesu cakkhuma; ","tha-ap544:1.3":"Ito satasahassamhi, ","tha-ap544:1.4":"kappe uppajji nayako. ","tha-ap544:2.1":"Sihahanu brahmagiro, ","tha-ap544:2.2":"hamsadundubhinissano; ","tha-ap544:2.3":"Nagavikkantagamano, ","tha-ap544:2.4":"candasuradikappabho. ","tha-ap544:3.1":"Mahamati mahaviro, ","tha-ap544:3.2":"mahajhayi mahabalo; ","tha-ap544:3.3":"Mahakaruniko natho, ","tha-ap544:3.4":"mahatamapanudano. ","tha-ap544:4.1":"Sa kadaci tilokaggo, ","tha-ap544:4.2":"veneyyam vinayam bahum; ","tha-ap544:4.3":"Dhammam desesi sambuddho, ","tha-ap544:4.4":"sattasayavidu muni. ","tha-ap544:5.1":"Jhayim jhanaratam viram, ","tha-ap544:5.2":"upasantam anavilam; ","tha-ap544:5.3":"Vannayanto parisatim, ","tha-ap544:5.4":"tosesi janatam jino. ","tha-ap544:6.1":"Tadaham hamsavatiyam, ","tha-ap544:6.2":"brahmano vedaparagu; ","tha-ap544:6.3":"Dhammam sutvana mudito, ","tha-ap544:6.4":"tam thanamabhipatthayim. ","tha-ap544:7.1":"Tada jino viyakasi, ","tha-ap544:7.2":"sanghamajjhe vinayako; ","tha-ap544:7.3":"‘Mudito hohi tvam brahme, ","tha-ap544:7.4":"lacchase tam manoratham. ","tha-ap544:8.1":"Satasahassito kappe, ","tha-ap544:8.2":"okkakakulasambhavo; ","tha-ap544:8.3":"Gotamo nama gottena, ","tha-ap544:8.4":"sattha loke bhavissati. ","tha-ap544:9.1":"Tassa dhammesu dayado, ","tha-ap544:9.2":"oraso dhammanimmito; ","tha-ap544:9.3":"Revato nama namena, ","tha-ap544:9.4":"hessati satthu savako’. ","tha-ap544:10.1":"Tena kammena sukatena, ","tha-ap544:10.2":"cetanapanidhihi ca; ","tha-ap544:10.3":"Jahitva manusam deham, ","tha-ap544:10.4":"tavatimsamagacchaham. ","tha-ap544:11.1":"Pacchime ca bhave dani, ","tha-ap544:11.2":"jatoham koliye pure; ","tha-ap544:11.3":"Khattiye kulasampanne, ","tha-ap544:11.4":"iddhe phite mahaddhane. ","tha-ap544:12.1":"Yada kapilavatthusmim, ","tha-ap544:12.2":"buddho dhammamadesayi; ","tha-ap544:12.3":"Tada pasanno sugate, ","tha-ap544:12.4":"pabbajim anagariyam. ","tha-ap544:13.1":"Kankha me bahula asi, ","tha-ap544:13.2":"kappakappe tahim tahim; ","tha-ap544:13.3":"Sabbam tam vinayi buddho, ","tha-ap544:13.4":"desetva dhammamuttamam. ","tha-ap544:14.1":"Tatoham tinnasamsaro, ","tha-ap544:14.2":"sada jhanasukhe rato; ","tha-ap544:14.3":"Viharami tada buddho, ","tha-ap544:14.4":"mam disva etadabravi. ","tha-ap544:15.1":"‘Ya kaci kankha idha va huram va, ","tha-ap544:15.2":"Sakavediya va paravediya va; ","tha-ap544:15.3":"Ye jhayino ta pajahanti sabba, ","tha-ap544:15.4":"Atapino brahmacariyam caranta’. ","tha-ap544:16.1":"Satasahasse katam kammam, ","tha-ap544:16.2":"phalam dassesi me idha; ","tha-ap544:16.3":"Sumutto saravegova, ","tha-ap544:16.4":"kilese jhapayim mama. ","tha-ap544:17.1":"Tato jhanaratam disva, ","tha-ap544:17.2":"buddho lokantagu muni; ","tha-ap544:17.3":"Jhayinam bhikkhunam aggo, ","tha-ap544:17.4":"pannapeti mahamati. ","tha-ap544:18.1":"Kilesa jhapita mayham, ","tha-ap544:18.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap544:18.3":"viharami anasavo. ","tha-ap544:19.1":"Svagatam vata me asi, ","tha-ap544:19.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap544:19.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam. ","tha-ap544:20.1":"Patisambhida catasso, ","tha-ap544:20.2":"…pe… ","tha-ap544:20.3":"katam buddhassa sasanam”. ","tha-ap544:21.1":"Ittham sudam ayasma kankharevato thero ima gathayo abhasitthati. ","tha-ap544:22.1":"Kankharevatattherassapadanam dutiyam. "}